package:

    - pip
    - python >=3.7
  run:
    - appdirs
    - autograd
    - autoray
    - cachetools

    - numpy
    - pennylane-lightning >=0.23

    - retworkx
    - scipy
    - semantic_version ==2.6
    - toml
